      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
         <head>Scope and Contents of the Collection</head>
         <p>The <emph render="bold">Evarts G. Loomis Company Collection of Hydraulic Sheeter Drawings</emph> consists of copies of 16 drawings, a materials list, and instructions for installation, operations and maintenance related to a hydraulic sheeter. The drawings have either the Evarts G. Loomis Company or Arlington Works name. One drawing is labeled Standard Pyroxoloid Company.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      
